Alpha Dolphy::


Alpha dolphy continued telling Lynxiz all things that had happened 
since they arrived, and she commented about Condor and how he was 
captured by a group of bot that they named themselves Decepticos.


"Epyon coudln't do nothing... They menaced that they would kill him 
if we tried to rescue him... of course they want a ramsom and he have 
to wait until they tell us what do they want..." Alpha Dolphy shook 
her head with sadness "I have tha bad feeling that something wrong is 
happening... but I don't know what is it"
